---
import TechStack from './TechStack.astro';
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 antialiased">
    <div class="py-12 px-3 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-24 sm:px-4 lg:px-6">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            <h2 class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">I miei servizi</h2>
            <p class="font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-xl mb-5">Mi concentro su soluzioni web innovative e di qualità che garantiscono risultati concreti per la tua attività.</p>
            <a href="#contatti" class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-500 hover:underline">
                Scopri come posso aiutare la tua attività
                <svg class="ml-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-8 sm:mt-10">
            <div class="group h-full p-4 sm:p-6 bg-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-blue-200 dark:hover:border-blue-800">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-3 sm:mb-5 w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 lg:h-14 lg:w-14 dark:bg-blue-900/30 group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 text-blue-600 lg:w-7 lg:h-7 dark:text-blue-300 group-hover:text-white dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m8 8-4 4 4 4m8 0 4-4-4-4m-2-3-4 14"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Web Development</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-1.5 sm:space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Sviluppo frontend e backend
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Soluzioni personalizzate
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Tecnologie moderne ed efficienti
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="group h-full p-4 sm:p-6 bg-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-purple-200 dark:hover:border-purple-800">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-3 sm:mb-5 w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-100 lg:h-14 lg:w-14 dark:bg-purple-900/30 group-hover:bg-purple-600 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 text-purple-600 lg:w-7 lg:h-7 dark:text-purple-300 group-hover:text-white dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.005 10.19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v.233l5.998 3.464L18 11.423v-.232a1 1 0 1 1 2 0V12a1 1 0 0 1-.5.866l-6.997 4.042a1 1 0 0 1-1 0l-6.998-4.042a1 1 0 0 1-.5-.866v-.81a1 1 0 0 1 1-1ZM5 15.15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v.232l5.997 3.464 5.998-3.464v-.232a1 1 0 1 1 2 0v.81a1 1 0 0 1-.5.865l-6.998 4.042a1 1 0 0 1-1 0L4.5 17.824a1 1 0 0 1-.5-.866v-.81a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/><path d="M12.503 2.134a1 1 0 0 0-1 0L4.501 6.17A1 1 0 0 0 4.5 7.902l7.002 4.047a1 1 0 0 0 1 0l6.998-4.04a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.732l-6.997-4.042Z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-purple-600 dark:group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">UI/UX Design</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-1.5 sm:space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-purple-500 dark:text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Interfacce intuitive e moderne
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-purple-500 dark:text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Design responsive per tutti i dispositivi
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-purple-500 dark:text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Focus su accessibilità e usabilità
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="group h-full p-4 sm:p-6 bg-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-green-200 dark:hover:border-green-800">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-3 sm:mb-5 w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-full bg-green-100 lg:h-14 lg:w-14 dark:bg-green-900/30 group-hover:bg-green-600 transition-all duration-300">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6 text-green-600 lg:w-7 lg:h-7 dark:text-green-300 group-hover:text-white dark:group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4.5V19a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h15M7 14l4-4 4 4 5-5m0 0h-3.207M20 9v3.207"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold dark:text-white group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors duration-300">SEO & Best Practices</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-1.5 sm:space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Ottimizzazione per i motori di ricerca
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Performance e velocità di caricamento
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 sm:w-3.5 sm:h-3.5 mr-1.5 sm:mr-2 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10 .5a9.5 9.5 0 1 0 9.5 9.5A9.51 9.51 0 0 0 10 .5Zm3.707 8.207-4 4a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-2-2a1 1 0 0 1 1.414-1.414L9 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 1.414Z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Conformità agli standard web
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <TechStack/>
    </div>
</section>
